::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Both bots notice that the female between them was leaning on both of them. 
They were both excited.

"Hey! Where are you going?!" Bloodystrike exclaims, jerking the female and 
Reptilica away from a doorway.

"To my quarters, of course," Reptilica replies calmly, pulling her toward 
him, "She can warm up there. She's obvioustly cold."

Bloodsytrike growls, keeping a tight grip on the femmbot. "Why not my 
quarters?"

"Because she wouldn't like it there," Reptilica says, continuing to pull. 
Bloodystrike keeps pulling the other way.

"Yes she would. They're just the same as yours!"

Reptillica sighs. "Allright, let's take her to the lab. Zardus would probably 
want her there anyways."

Bloodystrike hostilly nods his agreement, the two bots carrying the femm off 
toward the lab, each one struggling to hold more of her than the other.
